      "comment": "MAXO MIGHTY (9) has had nearly two months off since tackling a Gold Chalice heat at Bathurst and has switched to the Jason Grimson yard in that time. Strikes at 50 per cent at this distance and is lightly raced with upside. Looks nicely placed. RAYS REDEMPTION (7) continued his good form at the latest appearance when he came from a similar barrier and finished 1.6 metres away in third at this circuit and distance, his fourth placing from his last five outings. Go well again. THERES WALLY (6) had to work when racing three wide here last start so did well to box on and finish only 2.4m from the winner. CHARLIES ACE NZ (3) came from this barrier to place here three back so may be competitive.",
